Text:
Heartbroken & Homicidal is the upcoming eighth studio album by Twiztid, set to be 
released on September 21, 2010. Some songs will have Stefanie Eulinberg from Kid Rock's 
Twisted Brown Trucker Band playing the drums and the female vocals.
